casebody.data:
Tyrone CAROLINA
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided November 14, 2018

Tyrone Carolina, self-represented, in support of the petition.

James M. Ralls, assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Tyrone Carolina's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 185 Conn. App. 902, 191 A.3d 1108 (2018), is denied.
